Name: Super Slinger
About the game: Hello soldier! The earth is under attack by some aliens, and we need your help! Grab whatever weapon is closest and move in! We need to bring them down, and send them back home! I'm calling you since you are trained to fight in rough areas unlike the rest of us. Forests, Deserts, and Tundra are being taken over, so please! Get over here! Features: Juicy jumping and dashing Arcade like gameplay Arena fighting Progressive difficulty 4 big levels and 4 bosses Bullet hell type boss fights Funny enemy and player design Please soldier, come quickly! Wait, you picked a slingshot? Why the heck would you pick that?!
